  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Refined Stellar Metal: Yellow",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "精炼星球金属：黄色",
    "TencentChinese": "精炼星球金属：黄色",
    "TraditionalChinese": "精製星體金屬：黃"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">chromatic metal</span>, generated by fusion in the heart of a star. Such stellar material ends up forming deposits in the crust of local planets.<br><br>Copper is found on planets orbiting <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">yellow stars</span>, and can be placed in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to create purified <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Chromatic Metal</span> for use in the manufacture of advanced technologies.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。这种恒星物质最终在当地行星的地壳中形成沉积物。<br><br>铜可在环绕<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黄色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>以供生产先进技术使用。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>在恒星的中心融合产生。这种恒星物质最终在当地行星的地壳中形成沉积物。<br><br>铜可在环绕<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黄色恒星</span>的行星上发现，可以放在<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>中制造出纯<span class=\"name name-stellar\">彩色金属</span>以供生产先进技术使用。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，恆星中心熔合時生成。這種恆星材料最後會沉積於該行星的地殼。<br><br>銅可見於環繞<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">黃色恆星</span>的星球，可放入<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>製成純化<span class=\"name name-stellar\">有色金屬</span>，再用來製作先進科技。"
  },
